OL,4,Cattack at mosque detained for ten years
OL,6,FA teenager inspired by Hitler who
OL,7,Fplanned to carry out a terrorist
OL,8,Fattack at a mosque in Scotland has
OL,9,Fbeen sentenced to ten years in custody.
OL,11,FThe 17-year-old had planned to set
OL,12,Ffire to a Muslim centre in Greenock,
OL,13,FInverclyde, after befriending the Imam
OL,14,Fand mapping out the building's
OL,15,Finterior on his phone.
OL,17,FIn January this year, police officers
OL,18,Fapprehended the youth, who was
OL,19,Fcarrying a camouflage military-style
OL,20,Frucksack as he tried to gain entry to
OL,21,Fthe building on Laird Street.
