OL,6,FInside the bag, they found a German-
OL,7,Fmanufactured Glock-type air pistol,
OL,8,Fammunition, ball bearings, gas
OL,9,Fcartridges and aerosol cans,
OL,10,Fprosecutors said.
OL,12,FHe was sentenced at the High Court in
OL,13,FGlasgow on Thursday after pleading
OL,14,Fguilty to two charges of terrorism,
OL,15,Fthe Crown Office said.
OL,17,FThe teenager, who cannot be named for
OL,18,Flegal reasons, was sentenced to ten
OL,19,Fyears in custody and eight years of
OL,20,Fsupervision on licence upon release.
