OL,6,FIn a sentencing statement, Lord
OL,7,FArthurson said: "What you had in mind
OL,8,Fwas what can properly be characterised
OL,9,Fas a quite diabolical atrocity
OL,10,Finvolving extreme violence and
OL,11,Fmultiple deaths. You even requested
OL,12,Fthat your attack be livestreamed.
OL,14,F"Your conduct was only stopped by your
OL,15,Farrest, when you were quite literally
OL,16,Fat the very door of the centre."
