OL,6,FA search of the teenager's home
OL,7,Ffollowing his arrest found Adolf
OL,8,FHitler's book Mein Kampf, a copy of
OL,9,Fthe Quran, airsoft weapons, knives,
OL,10,Fmasks and instructions and ingredients
OL,11,Fto manufacture explosives.
OL,13,FHe also had a list on his mobile phone
OL,14,Fof individuals who had inspired his
OL,15,Fpolitical beliefs, including Hitler,
OL,16,FBenito Mussolini and Norwegian mass
OL,17,Fmurderer Anders Breivik, prosecutors
OL,18,Fsaid.
