OL,6,FAssistant Chief Constable Stuart
OL,7,FHouston, of Police Scotland, said: "I
OL,8,Fwant to pay tribute to the local
OL,9,Fofficers who took swift action to
OL,10,Fprotect the public and apprehended the
OL,11,Fyouth, as the potential consequences
OL,12,Fof his actions could have been
OL,13,Fextremely serious and had a profound
OL,14,Feffect on the local community.
