OL,6,F"This was a fast-moving and
OL,7,Fcomplicated inquiry, and officers
OL,8,Fcarried out a diligent and thorough
OL,9,Finvestigation to gather the evidence
OL,10,Fand brought him to court, which will
OL,11,Fnow see him face the consequences of
OL,12,Fhis intentions.
OL,14,F"Keeping our communities safe from
OL,15,Facts of terrorism remains a priority
OL,16,Ffor Police Scotland and its officers.
OL,17,FI also want to express my gratitude to
OL,18,Fthe partners who worked with us during
OL,19,Fthis inquiry to ensure the achievement
OL,20,Fof this objective is realised.
